# Dependency Guard

Use `ai-skills/skills/dependency-guard/SKILL.md`.

## Routing

- Go module changes
- Docker build changes
- CI build/test changes
- Shared dependency or shared-lib version changes
- `go.work`, `replace`, vendoring, or readonly build behavior

## Rules

1. Do not allow local-only dependency behavior to mask CI failures.
2. Avoid `go mod tidy` inside Dockerfiles or production build paths.
3. Prefer readonly, reproducible builds.
4. Verify dependency changes with the smallest relevant build/test evidence.
